strings.Value: {n}You hear a loud altercation from the street. In the middle of the village, Kagar the Rattler and Chieftain Vesket are yelling at each other.{/n}
"You don't understand, bonehead! There no Stishchak! Evil spirit trick you, and you believe like stupid child! You almost destroy whole tribe!"

"Stishchak lead Longtails to victory! We conquer all, and all be scared of us! Just a little more, I capture all lands, build great empire. Like old times! Like your song tells, from big water to high mountain!"
{n}Seeing you, Vesket bares his teeth.{/n} "Traitor! You work with warmblood! To kill Great Ancestor! Never forget! Revenge! Revenge!"
